# 06d1a7a
- added a resolver to squeeze in between parsing phase and
interpreting phase to bind identifiers (var/fun) to their
"correct" environment to refine `closure` and for future
functionalities.

# 2aac662
- added classes, with instance creation, properties and methods,
`this` object, constructors.
- expanded the list of supported statements, now include
